com.bmwcarit.barefoot.spatial

Interface SpatialIndex<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Result types depend on the implementation.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    QuadTreeIndex

    public interface SpatialIndex<T>
    Interface of spatial index for searching objects by means of spatial properties. There may be different implementations of this interface providing different underlying data structures for efficient data access, e.g. Quad-tree (see QuadTreeIndex) or R-Tree (not implemented yet).

      • nearest

        Set<T> nearest(com.esri.core.geometry.Point c)
        Gets nearest object stored in the index, which may be nevertheless multiple results if they have the same distance.
        Parameters:

              double r)
        Gets objects stored in the index that are within a certain radius or overlap a certain radius.
        Parameters:
        c - Center point for radius search.
        r - Radius in meters.
        Returns:
